#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GCompris is a multi-activity educational software. This documentation is for "
"the gcompris-teachers administration tool we provide."
msgstr ""
"GCompris je višenamjenski obrazovni softver. Ova dokumentacija služi za "
"korištenje gcompris-teachers administrativnog alata."

#. Tag: keyword
